{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "01", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "09", "M": "43", "S": "39"}}, "news": [{"title": "Allocate 2BHK houses by May-end: Telangana housing minister", "para": "Housing Minister Ponguleti Srinivas Reddy has ordered officials to allocate double-bedroom houses by May's end, prioritizing those nearing completion. Partially built homes will receive up to \u20b95 lakh aid, with beneficiaries allowed to finish construction if contractors refuse. Ineligible occupants will be removed, ensuring poverty remains the key eligibility factor.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/telangana-housing-minister-orders-allocation-of-2bhk-houses-by-may-end/130674018?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-26590/130674018.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Concorde leases 1.4 lakh sq ft space to BHIVE in Bengaluru; TEC adds 90,000 sq ft in Mumbai & Pune", "para": "Concorde has leased out 1.4 lakh sq ft to BHIVE Workspaces in Bengaluru, creating room for more than 3,000 professionals. On the other hand, The Executive Centre is gearing up for growth, with plans to unveil new locations in Mumbai and Pune, expanding its co-working offerings significantly.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/concorde-leases-1-4-lakh-sq-ft-space-to-bhive-in-bengaluru-tec-adds-90000-sq-ft-in-mumbai-pune/130673823?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-222474/130673823.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Uttar Pradesh to upgrade 100 more small towns under phase-II of aspirational towns scheme", "para": "Uttar Pradesh government is launching the second phase of its aspirational towns programme. This initiative will upgrade 100 more backward urban local bodies. The scheme foc